import PropTypes from 'prop-types'
import {
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_CONFIRMED,
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_FAILED,
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_PENDING,
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_TIMED_OUT,
} from './activity-statuses'

export const ActivityStatusType = PropTypes.oneOf([
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_CONFIRMED,
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_FAILED,
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_PENDING,
  ACTIVITY_STATUS_TIMED_OUT,
])
